## Wording
{{/markdown}}

<dl>
  <dt>Action + Object</dt>
  <dd>Use this format to clarify what will happen when the action is triggered. Default labels for buttons should be in the form <kbd>action + object type</kbd>, such as <em>Save Calendar</em>.</dd>

  <dt>Space constraints</dt>
  <dd>If there is a space constraint, label a button only with the action (<em>Save</em>).</dd>

  <dt>Articles</dt>
  <dd>By default, articles should not be used in labels. Use the article only when it is necessary to communicate the function of the button (<em>Release to Departments</em>).</dd>
</dl>
